  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this international multicenter, patient and outcome-assessor blinded
      randomized controlled trial is to determine whether the application of an individualized high
      PEEP strategy, aiming at avoiding an increase in the driving pressure during intraoperative
      ventilation, protects against the development of postoperative pulmonary complications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
